test_all_negative_one_range:
assert [-1, -1] == []
  Left contains 2 more items, first extra item: -1
  Full diff:
  - []
  + [-1, -1]
test_list_of_even_numbers:
assert [-30, -50] == [-20, -30, -40, -50]
  At index 0 diff: -30 != -20
  Right contains 2 more items, first extra item: -40
  Full diff:
  - [-20, -30, -40, -50]
  + [-30, -50]
test_negative_odd_range:
assert [-5, -9] == []
  Left contains 2 more items, first extra item: -5
  Full diff:
  - []
  + [-5, -9]
